  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You are skilled at dragging foes around the battlefield.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Power Attack, base attack bonus +1.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You do not provoke an attack of opportunity when performing a drag combat maneuver. In addition, you receive a +2 bonus on checks made to drag a foe. You also receive a +2 bonus to your Combat Maneuver Defense when an opponent tries to drag you.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>You provoke an attack of opportunity when performing a drag combat maneuver.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you are the target of a drag combat maneuver, you can spend a number of stamina points up to your Strength or Dexterity bonus, whichever is greater. Your CMD against that drag attempt increases by that number.",
